  "keyFeatures": [
    "Volo.Abp.Core runtime: AbpApplicationBase, modules, DI, dynamic proxy, options, exception handling, threading",
    "Modularity system (AbpModule, IAbpModule, dependency graph, plug-ins)",
    "Dependency Injection conventions (transient/scoped/singleton attributes, ConventionalRegistrar)",
    "Dynamic proxy + interceptors (Castle.Core integration)",
    "Volo.Abp.Ddd.Domain.Shared / Domain / Application / Application.Contracts layers",
    "Entities, aggregate roots, ValueObject, ICreationAuditedObject etc.",
    "IRepository and BasicRepositoryBase, specifications",
    "ApplicationService, CrudAppService, DTOs, AutoMap attributes",
    "Volo.Abp.Data: IDataSeeder, IDataFilter, IConnectionStringResolver, IGuidGenerator",
    "Unit of Work (Volo.Abp.Uow): IUnitOfWork, UnitOfWorkInterceptor",
    "Multi-tenancy (Volo.Abp.MultiTenancy, AspNetCore.MultiTenancy, tenant resolvers, configuration store)",
    "Authorization (permissions, policies, requirements, dynamic claims)",
    "Permission management module + provider model",
    "Feature management + Global Features",
    "Setting management + setting providers",
    "Auditing (AuditLog, AuditingInterceptor) + Audit Logging module",
    "Localization (resources, virtual files JSON, contributors)",
    "Validation + FluentValidation integration",
    "Caching (IDistributedCache abstractions, hybrid cache, Redis)",
    "Event Bus local + distributed (RabbitMQ, Kafka, Azure Service Bus, Rebus, Dapr)",
    "Background Jobs (default, Hangfire, Quartz, RabbitMQ, TickerQ)",
    "Background Workers (default, Hangfire, Quartz, TickerQ)",
    "Distributed Locking (abstractions, Dapr)",
    "BLOB Storing (FileSystem, Azure, AWS, Aliyun, Google, Minio, Bunny, Memory, Database)",
    "Emailing + MailKit",
    "SMS sending (abstractions, Aliyun, Tencent Cloud)",
    "Text templating (Core, Razor, Scriban)",
    "Virtual File System (embedded resources, physical files)",
    "Object mapping (AutoMapper, Mapperly)",
    "JSON serialization (System.Text.Json, Newtonsoft)",
    "Timing + IClock",
    "Imaging (Abstractions, ImageSharp, MagickNet, SkiaSharp, AspNetCore)",
    "Dapr integration (event bus, distributed locking, http client)",
    "GDPR abstractions, Object Extending, MultiLingualObjects, Specifications, Threading",
    "ASP.NET Core integration (Abstractions, MVC, MVC.UI, Bundling, Widgets, SignalR, Serilog, TestBase)",
    "ASP.NET Core authentication: JwtBearer, OAuth, OpenIdConnect",
    "Swashbuckle / API Versioning integration",
    "HTTP client framework + dynamic remote service proxies (IdentityModel, Web, Dapr)",
    "MVC / Razor Pages UI: Bootstrap tag helpers, Theme Shared, Widgets, Navigation, Minify, Multi-Tenancy UI",
    "Blazor UI: Components Web/Server/WebAssembly/MauiBlazor + Theming + Bundling",
    "BlazoriseUI base components",
    "MAUI client + Autofac WebAssembly",
    "Identity module (users, roles, OUs, security log, sessions, passkeys, external login)",
    "Account module (login UI, profile, registration, IdentityServer & OpenIddict variants)",
    "Permission management module (DB-backed permission providers)",
    "Setting management module (DB-backed setting providers)",
    "Feature management module (DB-backed feature providers)",
    "Tenant management module",
    "Audit logging module (Domain, EFCore, MongoDB persistence)",
    "Background jobs module (Domain persistence)",
    "Blob storing database module",
    "CmsKit module (blogs, pages, menus, comments, reactions, tags, ratings, marked items, media)",
    "Blogging module",
    "OpenIddict module",
    "IdentityServer module (legacy)",
    "Users abstractions module",
    "Virtual File Explorer module",
    "Basic Theme module",
    "Client simulation module",
    "Docs module (Volo.Docs)",
    "Angular packages: @abp/ng.core, components, theme-shared, theme-basic, oauth, account(-core), identity, permission/setting/feature/tenant-management, cms-kit, generators, schematics",
    "JS packs (npm/packs) for jQuery, Bootstrap, DataTables, Toastr, Sweetalert2, Luxon, Moment, Markdown-it, ChartJS, etc.",
    "ABP CLI: New, Update, AddModule, AddPackage, GenerateProxy, Bundle, InstallLibs, Suite, Translate, Mcp, Login/Logout, SwitchTo*",
    "CLI core: Project Building, Project Modification, Service Proxying (Angular/CSharp/JavaScript), Templates, Github, Licensing, Bundling",
    "Startup templates: app (aspnet-core + angular), app-nolayers, module, console, maui, wpf",
    "Testing: AbpTestBase, AspNetCore.TestBase, hundreds of test projects per package",
    "Build scripts (PowerShell), Directory.Build.props, Directory.Packages.props",
    "NPM publishing scripts (publish-mvc.ps1, publish-ng.ps1)",
    "Deploy scripts (fetch-and-build, nuget-pack/push, npm-publish, github-release)",
    "Tools: changelog-generator, localization-key-synchronizer, nuget tools",
    "AI rules (.mdc) for coding agents: abp-core, application-layer, ddd-patterns, ef-core, mongodb, mvc, blazor, angular, testing patterns"
  ],
